{"履修期": "春学期", "主な教授言語": "ドイツ語", "授業目的": "<p style=\"font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-stretch:normal;font-size:12.7px;line-height:normal;font-family:Arial;font-size-adjust:none;font-kerning:auto;font-variant-alternates:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-numeric:normal;font-variant-east-asian:normal;font-variant-position:normal;font-variant-emoji:normal;font-feature-settings:normal;font-optical-sizing:auto;font-variation-settings:normal;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-color:rgb(0,0,0);\"><span style=\"font-size:12.67px;font-kerning:none;\">Nachhaltigkeit und deutschsprachige Literatur.</span><span style=\"font-size:12.67px;font-kerning:none;\">&nbsp;</span><span ｍｓ=\"ｍｓ\" 明朝\";font-size:12px;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;\"=\"明朝';font-size:12px;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;'\" style=\"font-size:12.7px;\">「環境保護国ドイツ」を文学史的に検証する</span></p><p style=\"font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-stretch:normal;font-size:12.7px;line-height:normal;font-family:Arial;font-size-adjust:none;font-kerning:auto;font-variant-alternates:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-numeric:normal;font-variant-east-asian:normal;font-variant-position:normal;font-variant-emoji:normal;font-feature-settings:normal;font-optical-sizing:auto;font-variation-settings:normal;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-color:rgb(0,0,0);\"><span style=\"font-size:12.67px;\">In diesem Kurs sprechen wir über verschiedene Aspekte von Nachhaltigkeit (サステナビリティ), über die Rolle, die Umweltschutz in Deutschland spielt, und ob literarische Werke zu ökologischem Verhalten motivieren können.&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-stretch:normal;font-size:12.7px;line-height:normal;font-family:Arial;font-size-adjust:none;font-kerning:auto;font-variant-alternates:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-numeric:normal;font-variant-east-asian:normal;font-variant-position:normal;font-variant-emoji:normal;font-feature-settings:normal;font-optical-sizing:auto;font-variation-settings:normal;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-color:rgb(0,0,0);\"><span style=\"font-size:12.67px;\">「サステナビリティ」のさまざまな側面、ドイツの環境保護意識の役割、また、文学テクストがエコロジー活動を促進する可能性について、作品の読解と議論を通じて考える。</span></p>", "到達目標": "<p style=\"font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-stretch:normal;font-size:12.7px;line-height:normal;font-family:Arial;font-size-adjust:none;font-kerning:auto;font-variant-alternates:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-numeric:normal;font-variant-east-asian:normal;font-variant-position:normal;font-variant-emoji:normal;font-feature-settings:normal;font-optical-sizing:auto;font-variation-settings:normal;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-color:rgb(0,0,0);\"><span style=\"font-size:12.67px;font-kerning:none;\">Deutschland hat ein umweltfreundliches Image, aber wird es dem auch gerecht?</span></p>\n<p style=\"font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-stretch:normal;font-size:12.7px;line-height:normal;font-family:Arial;font-size-adjust:none;font-kerning:auto;font-variant-alternates:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-numeric:normal;font-variant-east-asian:normal;font-variant-position:normal;font-variant-emoji:normal;font-feature-settings:normal;font-optical-sizing:auto;font-variation-settings:normal;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-color:rgb(0,0,0);\"><span style=\"font-size:12.67px;font-kerning:none;\">Die Studierenden beschäftigen sich mit Auszügen aus verschiedenen Textformen -- Sachtexte sowie literarische Texte (beispielsweise von E.T.A Hoffmann, Erich Kästner, Irmgard Keun, Heinrich Böll, Bernhard Schlink, Arno Geiger u. a.) -- und gewinnen einen Einblick in nachhaltige Praktiken der Vergangenheit, historische Entwicklungen im Umweltschutz und Zukunftsszenarien.&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-stretch:normal;font-size:12.7px;line-height:normal;font-family:Arial;font-size-adjust:none;font-kerning:auto;font-variant-alternates:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-numeric:normal;font-variant-east-asian:normal;font-variant-position:normal;font-variant-emoji:normal;font-feature-settings:normal;font-optical-sizing:auto;font-variation-settings:normal;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-color:rgb(0,0,0);\"><span style=\"font-size:12.67px;font-kerning:none;\">Sie erweitern dabei ihren deutschen Wortschatz und ihre Kommunikationsfähigkeit.</span></p><p class=\"s6\" style=\"line-height:1.91;font-size:12px;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;\"><span class=\"s7\" ｍｓ=\"ｍｓ\" 明朝\";\"=\"明朝';'\" style=\"line-height:14.4px;font-family:;\">ドイツには環境保護の先進国というイメージがあるが、そのイメージはいつから形成されたのか、またどの程度正しいのかを、近現代文学</span><span class=\"s7\" ｍｓ=\"ｍｓ\" 明朝\";\"=\"明朝';'\" style=\"line-height:14.4px;font-family:;\">の作品に即して歴史的・批判的に考察する。</span></p><p class=\"s6\" style=\"line-height:1.91;font-size:12px;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;\"><span class=\"s7\" ｍｓ=\"ｍｓ\" 明朝\";\"=\"明朝';'\" style=\"line-height:14.4px;font-family:;\">また、このテーマについてのドイツ語の語彙を学び、コミュニケーション力の向上も図る。</span></p>", "特記事項": "", "関連科目": "", "授業の概要・背景": "", "授業方法": "<div><p style=\"font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-stretch:normal;font-size:12.7px;line-height:normal;font-family:Arial;font-size-adjust:none;font-kerning:auto;font-variant-alternates:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-numeric:normal;font-variant-east-asian:normal;font-variant-position:normal;font-variant-emoji:normal;font-feature-settings:normal;font-optical-sizing:auto;font-variation-settings:normal;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-color:rgb(0,0,0);\"><span style=\"font-size:13.28px;\">授業は基本的にドイツ語で行い、</span><span style=\"font-size:13.28px;\">できる範囲でドイツ語でのディスカッションを試みたい。</span></p></div>", "トピック": {"第1回": ["<p style=\"font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-stretch:normal;font-size:12.7px;line-height:normal;font-family:Arial;font-size-adjust:none;font-kerning:auto;font-va